      <title>Sky 称 Cineworld 所有者考虑在美国上市连锁影院</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-17/cineworld-owners-consider-us-listing-for-cinema-chain-sky-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据天空新闻周日报道，Cineworld 的所有者正考虑将这家连锁电影院——该电影院于 2023 年离开伦敦证券交易所——于 2026 年在纽约上市。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-17/cineworld-owners-consider-us-listing-for-cinema-chain-sky-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 17 Nov 2024 16:58:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
